<style>
button {
width: 200;
height: 100;
background-color: #009900;
font-size: 20px;
color: white;
text-align:center;
border-radius: 12px;
font_family:"Engravers MT"
}
    </style>

<button onclick="getLocation()">SHARE LOCATION WITH FIRST RESPONDERS</button>
<p id="demo"></p>
<script>
var x = document.getElementById("demo");
function logError(error) {
    console.log(error);
}
function getLocation() {
  if (navigator.geolocation) {
    console.log("About to get location");
    navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition(showPosition, logError);
    console.log("Got location");
  } else { 
    console.log("Will not get location");
    x.innerHTML = "Geolocation is not supported by this browser.";
  }
}
function showPosition(position) {
  console.log("About to display location");
  x.innerHTML = "Latitude: " + position.coords.latitude + 
  "<br>Longitude: " + position.coords.longitude;
}
</script>

data-code="&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html lang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
  &lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot;&gt;
  &lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&quot; content=&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&quot;&gt;
  &lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;X-UA-Compatible&quot; content=&quot;ie=edge&quot;&gt;
  &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-alpha.6/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot; integrity=&quot;sha384-rwoIResjU2yc3z8GV/NPeZWAv56rSmLldC3R/AZzGRnGxQQKnKkoFVhFQhNUwEyJ&quot; crossorigin=&quot;anonymous&quot;&gt;
  &lt;script src=&quot;https://unpkg.com/axios/dist/axios.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
  &lt;title&gt;My Geocode App&lt;/title&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;container&quot;&gt;
    &lt;h2 id=&quot;text-center&quot;&gt;Enter Location: &lt;/h2&gt;
    &lt;form id=&quot;location-form&quot;&gt;
      &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; id=&quot;location-input&quot; class=&quot;form-control form-control-lg&quot;&gt;
      &lt;br&gt;
      &lt;button type=&quot;submit&quot; class=&quot;btn btn-primary btn-block&quot;&gt;Submit&lt;/button&gt;
    &lt;/form&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;card-block&quot; id=&quot;formatted-address&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;card-block&quot; id=&quot;address-components&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;card-block&quot; id=&quot;geometry&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;script&gt;
    // Call Geocode
    //geocode();

    // Get location form
    var locationForm = document.getElementById(&#39;location-form&#39;);

    // Listen for submiot
    locationForm.addEventListener(&#39;submit&#39;, geocode);

    function geocode(e){
      // Prevent actual submit
      e.preventDefault();

      var location = document.getElementById(&#39;location-input&#39;).value;

      axios.get(&#39;https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/geocode/json&#39;,{
        params:{
          address:location,
          key:&#39;AIzaSyB6PjZbi9N2VE6bmaK6J2ZSxMbLTKMKJH4&#39;
        }
      })
      .then(function(response){
        // Log full response
        console.log(response);

        // Formatted Address
        var formattedAddress = response.data.results[0].formatted_address;
        var formattedAddressOutput = `
          &lt;ul class=&quot;list-group&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li class=&quot;list-group-item&quot;&gt;${formattedAddress}&lt;/li&gt;
          &lt;/ul&gt;
        `;

        // Address Components
        var addressComponents = response.data.results[0].address_components;
        var addressComponentsOutput = &#39;&lt;ul class=&quot;list-group&quot;&gt;&#39;;
        for(var i = 0;i &lt; addressComponents.length;i++){
          addressComponentsOutput += `
            &lt;li class=&quot;list-group-item&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;${addressComponents[i].types[0]}&lt;/strong&gt;: ${addressComponents[i].long_name}&lt;/li&gt;
          `;
        }
        addressComponentsOutput += &#39;&lt;/ul&gt;&#39;;

        // Geometry
        var lat = response.data.results[0].geometry.location.lat;
        var lng = response.data.results[0].geometry.location.lng;
        var geometryOutput = `
          &lt;ul class=&quot;list-group&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li class=&quot;list-group-item&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Latitude&lt;/strong&gt;: ${lat}&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li class=&quot;list-group-item&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Longitude&lt;/strong&gt;: ${lng}&lt;/li&gt;
          &lt;/ul&gt;
        `;

        // Output to app
        document.getElementById(&#39;formatted-address&#39;).innerHTML = formattedAddressOutput;
        document.getElementById(&#39;address-components&#39;).innerHTML = addressComponentsOutput;
        document.getElementById(&#39;geometry&#39;).innerHTML = geometryOutput;
      })
      .catch(function(error){
        console.log(error);
      });
    }
  &lt;/script&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
